title: Angel and Faith 1 - 23 (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is a pack of all the back issues of Angel and Faith bringing it current to June 2013. Since there seem to be so many missing issues out there and people looking for them. I will keep this in my seedbox until at least the end of the month to give people time to complete their collections.

Please don't hit and run and if possible take more than you need to provide enough seeds for everyone else.

All credit goes to the original scanners. I just adjusted the resolution and compressed the files for easier reading on tablets and ereaders as well as to save on hard drive space. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the file names to avoid confusion.

Enjoy!
